subscribe to YouTube TV, the platform announced. Just as multiview on NFL Sunday Ticket enables audiences to watch four different games at once, the feature for Coachella", "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/4/24121421/youtube-tv-coachella-2024-multiview-four-stages-livestream", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 100, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source": "https://www.theverge.com/rss/index.xml", "source_obj__id": 359, "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "YouTube is bringing NFL-style multiview to Coachella 2024\u2019s livestream", "user": null, "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-04-04T20:52:14+00:00", "description": "<figure>\n      <img alt=\"The Instagram icon is featured in the middle of a background filled with pink, orange, and purple shapes.\" src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/c38AvcHFXeEY3Jw7jPK02nNgLCs=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73256444/VRG_Illo_K_Radtke_STK070_Instagram_1.0.jpg\" />\n        <figcaption>Illustration by Kristen Radtke / The Verge</figcaption>\n    </figure>\n\n  <p id=\"dBHTyz\">Yesterday, I reported that Meta\u2019s AI image generator <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/3/24120029/instagram-meta-ai-sticker-generator-asian-people-racism\">was making everyone Asian</a>, even when the text prompt specified another race. Today, I briefly had the opposite problem: I was unable to generate <em>any </em>Asian people using the same prompts as the day before.</p>\n<p id=\"tChNAy\">The tests I did yesterday were on Instagram, via the AI image generator available in direct messages. After dozens of tries, I was unable to generate a single accurate image", "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/4/24121419/meta-instagram-ai-image-generator-asian-race", "manual_status_code": 0, "